data.description: Discover the epitome of East El Paso living. This 1,665 spacious sq/ft, Tropicana-built gem offers 3-bedrooms ALL DOWNSTAIRS, with an upstairs loft.  Home has the comfort and convenience of refrigerated air, mudroom/washroom via the 2-car garage. This back yard offers privacy with the raised rock wall all around and a lighted patio/pergola for entertaining and family nights.  School and neighborhood park nearby.  Perfect starter home.  Home is occupied.
